Telecomando CamKix
<img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1114722 aligncenter" title="Fare foto con iPhone, i migliori accessori" src="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2021/11/CamKix-Telecomando--391x480.jpg.webp" alt="Fare foto con iPhone, i migliori accessori" width="391" height="480" srcset="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2021/11/CamKix-Telecomando--391x480.jpg.webp 391w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2021/11/CamKix-Telecomando--978x1200.jpg.webp 978w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2021/11/CamKix-Telecomando--24x30.jpg.webp 24w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2021/11/CamKix-Telecomando--61x75.jpg.webp 61w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2021/11/CamKix-Telecomando--90x110.jpg.webp 90w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2021/11/CamKix-Telecomando--130x160.jpg.webp 130w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2021/11/CamKix-Telecomando--408x500.jpg.webp 408w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2021/11/CamKix-Telecomando--41x50.jpg.webp 41w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2021/11/CamKix-Telecomando--82x100.jpg.webp 82w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2021/11/CamKix-Telecomando--163x200.jpg.webp 163w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2021/11/CamKix-Telecomando--696x854.jpg.webp 696w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2021/11/CamKix-Telecomando--1068x1310.jpg.webp 1068w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2021/11/CamKix-Telecomando--342x420.jpg.webp 342w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2021/11/CamKix-Telecomando-.jpg.webp 1223w" sizes="(max-width: 391px) 100vw, 391px" />
Costa pochissimo, ma potrebbe risultare utile in moltissimi contesti. CamKix è un semplice e piccolo telecomando bluetooth, che vi permetterà di scattare foto senza avere lo smartphone tra le mani.
Può essere attaccato al portachiavi, e risultare sempre disponibile al bisogno. Premendo i tasti sul piccolo telecomando riuscirete a scattare foto in remoto: ottima per le foto di gruppo.
